        </linkGrp>
        <div n="M11017H2">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-M11017H2-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-M11017H2-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-M11017H2-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">By Dr. D<hi rend="small-caps">ELANY</hi><ref target="#spp-M11017H2-footnote-headnote-1">1</ref><note n="1" xml:id="spp-M11017H2-footnote-headnote-1" place="foot">See the Dean's poetical epistle to this gentleman, vol. VIII. part ii. p. 170. He was many years dean of <hi rend="italics">Down</hi> and died <hi rend="italics">May</hi> 7, 1768, aged 83. N</note>.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-M11017H2-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-M11017H2-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-M11017H2-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-M11017H2-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-M11017H2-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-M11017H2-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">'T</hi>IS so old, and so ugly, and yet so convenient,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-2" n="2">You're sometimes in pleasure, though often in pain in't.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-3" n="3">'Tis so large you may lodge a few friends with ease in't,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-4" n="4">You may turn and stretch at your length, if you please, in't;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-5" n="5">'Tis so little, the family live in a press in't,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-6" n="6">And poor lady <hi rend="italics">Betty</hi> <note place="foot">·Daughter of the earl of <hi rend="italics">Droghede</hi>, and married to <hi rend="italics">George Rochfort</hi>, esq. N.</note> has scarce room to dress in't;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-7" n="7">'Tis so cold in the winter, you can't bear to lie in't,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-8" n="8">And so hot in the summer, you're ready to fry in't;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-9" n="9">'Tis so brittle 'twould scarce bear the weight of a tun,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-10" n="10">Yet so staunch, that it keeps out a great deal of sun;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-11" n="11">'Tis so crazy, the weather with ease beats quite through it,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-12" n="12">And you're forc'd every year in some part to renew it;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-13" n="13">'Tis so ugly, so useful, so big, and so little,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-14" n="14">'Tis so staunch, and so crazy, so strong, and so brittle,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-15" n="15">'Tis at one time so hot, and another so cold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-16" n="16">It is part of the new, and part of the old;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-17" n="17">It is just half a blessing, and just half a curse──</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-M11017H2-line-18" n="18">I wish then, dear <hi rend="italics">George</hi>, it were better or worse.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
